history.content:
The issues with students who had duplicated enrollment appointments are now fixed. 
Affected students received the exact enrollment appointments they were originally assigned as of Friday, September 28, to prevent them from receiving earlier or later appointments through the randomly generated algorithm.
If you're currently enrolled, your CalCentral doesn't say you're graduating this semester, and you're still missing an enrollment appointment, please contact sishelp@berkeley.edu
history.subject: Spring 2019 Enrollment Appointments Now Fixed
